column5: hey everybody,  in about an hr or so we'll be fighting the holiday weekend traffic up the 400 to Lakair for the first time.  hope to post a report when we get back.   ryan
Best of Luck Dunner.  Looking forward to see how you did. I'm heading back up to that general area in just over a month.
good luck  Joey and Paul show be showing up there too, say hi to them
They are there now and I wish I was too.  Have a great trip!
Lakair's a great place & your gonna luv it. We just got back from there a couple weeks ago.
Yup, Joey and Paul are there and on wifi at nights for hellos. Say hi to them and you have yourself a great time!
Yup, great place, just got back from there a few weeks ago. Say hi to the crew for me! Wish I was coming with you.
